videos.description: Michigan's Jordan Poole drives to the hoop and hits Austin Davis with a sweet no-look pass for the dunk.
videos.headline: Poole with a no-look, behind-the-back dish to Davis

videos.description: Michigan's Jordan Poole creates some separation from the defender with a quick step-back move and hits the three.
videos.headline: Poole hits step-back 3-pointer in defender's face

videos.description: Penn State's Mike Watkins steals the ball and gets the fast-break dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Watkins' steal leads to big dunk

videos.description: Michigan's Eli Brooks steals the ball for a monster dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks with the steal and breakaway dunk

videos.description: Michigan's Ignas Brazdeikis powers his way to the basket and makes a nice spin move for a layup which getting fouled.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis powers his way to an and-1 bucket
